{"tid":1476245,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外交部駐港特派員：當前事態絕非人權、自由與民主問題","createTime":"2019-08-15T18:04:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T18:16:58.000Z","uid":98673,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7a9ee79fc81273ef23da0aa03ecf8e809fcfd3d5","tid":1476245,"uid":98673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:04:42.000Z","msg":"外交部駐港特派員：當前事態絕非人權、自由與民主問題<br />\n<br />\n外交部駐港公署特派員謝鋒，出席一個論壇時表示，當前香港事態的本質，絕非所謂的人權、自由與民主問題，而是香港反對派和極端暴力分子，企圖以暴力等非法手段，顛覆特區合法政府、挑戰中央政府權威、動搖香港「一國兩制」的憲制根基，是外國干預勢力踐踏國際法和國際關係基本準則，企圖將香港作為一枚棋子，牽制和遏制中華民族偉大復興。謝鋒指出，近期個別國家及其駐港領事人員，插手香港事務、干涉中國內政的行為嚴重違反國際法。謝鋒又表示，當前香港面臨回歸22年來最危險、最嚴峻的局面，當務之急和壓倒一切的任務，就是止暴制亂、恢復秩序。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474945-20190816.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474945-20190816.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEhF66oQwccw1TbdUPfwT%2FAY%3D&h=35ae9f7e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474945-20190816.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=9794155e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474945-20190816.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"b7d535fe6ba617966cbd2e7ef2129c89585b73f4","tid":1476245,"uid":107478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:05:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DMh70kj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDMh70kj.jpg&h=2feb58bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PcjRHyE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPcjRHyE.jpg&h=932bd70a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n齊來參與instagram同facebook嘅 #全城㩒美元 #USDchallenge 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/l4FGKy0Nbz4Vdugz6/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.li